---
import Button from "./ui/Button.astro";

---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="text-center md:text-left">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-bold tracking-tight text-brand-dark">
              Tisser le lien citoyen. <br /> Révéler le <span class="text-brand-purple">KantoMG</span>.
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-text/80 max-w-xl mx-auto md:mx-0">
              Là où la sagesse des ancêtres éclaire les citoyens de demain. KantoMG est votre guide pour une citoyenneté active, nourrie par la richesse de notre culture.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
              <Button text="Télécharger l'application" href="#" size="large" />
              <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
                <a href="#" class="transition-transform hover:scale-105" aria-label="Download on the App Store">
                
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="transition-transform hover:scale-105" aria-label="Get it on Google Play">
           
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative h-full flex items-center justify-center -order-1 lg:order-1">
            <div class="relative mx-auto border-brand-dark/80 bg-brand-dark/80 border-[12px] rounded-[2.5rem] h-[550px] w-[280px] shadow-2xl shadow-brand-purple/30">
                <div class="w-[120px] h-[18px] bg-brand-dark/80 top-0 rounded-b-[1rem] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 absolute"></div>
                <div class="h-[40px] w-[3px] bg-brand-dark/80 absolute -start-[15px] top-[110px] rounded-s-lg"></div>
                <div class="h-[40px] w-[3px] bg-brand-dark/80 absolute -start-[15px] top-[160px] rounded-s-lg"></div>
                <div class="h-[56px] w-[3px] bg-brand-dark/80 absolute -end-[15px] top-[132px] rounded-e-lg"></div>
                <div class="rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden w-full h-full bg-brand-dark">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579546929518-9e396f3cc809?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="KantoMG App Screenshot" />
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>